---
// Piano Studio Chimica — 7 Giorni
---

<html lang="it">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Piano Studio Chimica — 7 Giorni</title>
  <style>
    * {
      font-family: 'Departure Mono', monospace;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html, body {
      background: #000;
      color: #fff;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    /* Scanline overlay */
    body::before {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background: repeating-linear-gradient(
        0deg,
        transparent,
        transparent 2px,
        rgba(255,255,255,0.012) 2px,
        rgba(255,255,255,0.012) 4px
      );
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 999;
    }

    .day-card {
      border: 1px solid #1e1e1e;
      transition: border-color 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease;
    }
    .day-card:hover {
      border-color: #333;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.015);
    }

    .badge {
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      padding: 2px 8px;
      border: 1px solid currentColor;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .tip-box {
      border-left: 2px solid #252525;
      color: #4a4a4a;
      font-size: 11px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .section-head {
      font-size: 9px;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      color: #333;
    }

    .topic-text {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .day-title {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #ccc;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }

    /* Fade-in stagger */
    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(8px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    .day-card { animation: fadeUp 0.45s ease both; }
    .day-card:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.05s; }
    .day-card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
    .day-card:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.15s; }
    .day-card:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
    .day-card:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.25s; }
    .day-card:nth-child(6) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
    .day-card:nth-child(7) { animation-delay: 0.35s; }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; }
      to   { opacity: 1; }
    }
    header { animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease both; }

    /* Responsive zoom: 150% at 2560px, scales down proportionally */
    :root { zoom: 1; }

    @media (min-width: 2560px) { :root { zoom: 1.5; } }
    @media (max-width: 2559px) and (min-width: 1920px) { :root { zoom: 1.125; } }
    @media (max-width: 1919px) and (min-width: 1440px) { :root { zoom: 1.0; } }
    @media (max-width: 1439px) and (min-width: 1024px) { :root { zoom: 0.9; } }
    @media (max-width: 1023px) and (min-width: 768px)  { :root { zoom: 0.8; } }
    @media (max-width: 767px)  and (min-width: 480px)  { :root { zoom: 0.7; } }
    @media (max-width: 479px)                          { :root { zoom: 0.6; } }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen bg-black px-5 py-14 md:px-12 lg:px-24">

  <!-- Header -->
  <header class="mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <p class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.18em] text-neutral-800 mb-3">[ PIANO DI STUDIO ]</p>
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl text-white tracking-tight leading-none mb-2">
      CHIMICA<br/>
      <span class="text-neutral-600">— 7 GIORNI</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-[10px] text-neutral-800 tracking-[0.2em] mt-4">SAB 21 → VEN 27 &nbsp;·&nbsp; OLIMPIADI / GARE</p>
    <div class="mt-7 border-t border-neutral-900"></div>
  </header>

  <!-- Cards -->
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-2">

    <!-- Day 1 — Atomo -->
    <div class="day-card p-5 rounded-none">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-4 flex-wrap">
        <span class="badge" style="color:#4a90d9;">SAB 21</span>
        <span class="day-title">Atomo, struttura e tavola periodica</span>
        <span class="text-[10px] text-neutral-800 tracking-widest ml-auto">~4–5h</span>
      </div>
      <p class="section-head mb-2">// MATTINA</p>
      <div class="flex gap-2 items-start mb-2">
        <span class="w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full mt-[5px] shrink-0" style="background:#378ADD;"></span>
        <span class="topic-text">Modelli atomici (Thomson, Rutherford, Bohr), isotopi, nucleo</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-2 items-start mb-2">
        <span class="w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full mt-[5px] shrink-0" style="background:#378ADD;"></span>
        <span class="topic-text">Atomo quantistico: orbitali, numeri quantici, configurazione elettronica</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-2 items-start mb-4">
        <span class="w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full mt-[5px] shrink-0" style="background:#378ADD;"></span>
        <span class="topic-text">Principio di Pauli, regola di Hund, livelli energetici</span>
      </div>
      <p class="section-head mb-2">// POMERIGGIO</p>
      <div class="flex gap-2 items-start mb-2">
        <span class="w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full mt-[5px] shrink-0" style="background:#1D9E75;"></span>
        <span class="topic-text">Tavola periodica: gruppi, periodi, blocchi, simboli di Lewis</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-2 items-start mb-4">
        <span class="w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full mt-[5px] shrink-0" style="background:#1D9E75;"></span>
        <span class="topic-text">Proprietà periodiche: raggio atomico, energia ionizzazione, affinità elettronica, elettronegatività</span>
      </div>
      <div class="tip-box pl-3 py-1">
        Esercitati a scrivere la configurazione elettronica degli elementi dei primi 4 periodi a memoria.
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Day 2 — Legami -->
    <div class="day-card p-5 rounded-none">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-4 flex-wrap">
        <span class="badge" style="color:#c9862a;">DOM 22</span>
        <span class="day-title">Legami chimici e forma delle molecole</span>
        <span class="text-[10px] text-neutral-800 tracking-widest ml-auto">~4–5h</span>
      </div>
      <p class="section-head mb-2">// MATTINA</p>
      <div class="flex gap-2 items-start mb-2">
        <span class="w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full mt-[5px] shrink-0" style="background:#BA7517;"></span>
        <span class="topic-text">Legame ionico, covalente (puro/polare), metallico — strutture di Lewis</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-2 items-start mb-4">
        <span class="w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full mt-[5px] shrink-0" style="background:#BA7517;"></span>
        <span class="topic-text">Solidi ionici, metallici, reticolari (diamante, grafite, quarzo)</span>
      </div>
      <p class="section-head mb-2">// POMERIGGIO</p>
      <div class="flex gap-2 items-start mb-2">
        <span class="w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full mt-[5px] shrink-0" style="background:#BA7517;"></span>
        <span class="topic-text">Teoria VSEPR → geometria molecolare (lineare, piana, tetraedrica, ecc.)</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-2 items-start mb-2">
        <span class="w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full mt-[5px] shrink-0" style="background:#BA7517;"></span>
        <span class="topic-text">Momento dipolare, molecole polari/apolari</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-2 items-start mb-4">
        <span class="w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full mt-[5px] shrink-0" style="background:#BA7517;"></span>
        <span class="topic-text">Forze intermolecolari: London, dipolo-dipolo, legame a idrogeno</span>
      </div>
      <div class="tip-box pl-3 py-1">
        Allena la VSEPR con H₂O, NH₃, CO₂, CH₄, SF₆, PCl₅ — spesso escono agli esami.
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Day 3 — Moli -->
    <div class="day-card p-5 rounded-none">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-4 flex-wrap">
        <span class="badge" style="color:#c44a72;">LUN 23</span>
        <span class="day-title">Moli, stechiometria e gas</span>
        <span class="text-[10px] text-neutral-800 tracking-widest ml-auto">~4–5h</span>
      </div>
      <p class="section-head mb-2">// MATTINA</p>
      <div class="flex gap-2 items-start mb-2">
        <span class="w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full mt-[5px] shrink-0" style="background:#D4537E;"></span>
        <span class="topic-text">Mole, costante di Avogadro, massa molare, volume molare</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-2 items-start mb-2">
        <span class="w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full mt-[5px] shrink-0" style="background:#D4537E;"></span>
        <span class="topic-text">Formula minima e molecolare, composizione percentuale</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-2 items-start mb-4">
        <span class="w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full mt-[5px] shrink-0" style="background:#D4537E;"></span>
        <span class="topic-text">Calcoli stechiometrici, reagente limitante, resa di reazione</span>
      </div>
      <p class="section-head mb-2">// POMERIGGIO</p>
      <div class="flex gap-2 items-start mb-2">
        <span class="w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full mt-[5px] shrink-0" style="background:#D4537E;"></span>
        <span class="topic-text">Leggi dei gas: Boyle, Charles, Gay-Lussac, principio Avogadro</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-2 items-start mb-4">
        <span class="w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full mt-[5px] shrink-0" style="background:#D4537E;"></span>
        <span class="topic-text">Equazione di stato dei gas ideali PV = nRT</span>
      </div>
      <div class="tip-box pl-3 py-1">
        Risolvi almeno 10 esercizi numerici sulla stechiometria — è la sezione con più calcoli alle gare.
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Day 4 — Nomenclatura -->
    <div class="day-card p-5 rounded-none">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-4 flex-wrap">
        <span class="badge" style="color:#6fa832;">MAR 24</span>
        <span class="day-title">Nomenclatura, soluzioni e prop. colligative</span>
        <span class="text-[10px] text-neutral-800 tracking-widest ml-auto">~4–5h</span>
      </div>
      <p class="section-head mb-2">// MATTINA</p>
      <div class="flex gap-2 items-start mb-4">
        <span class="w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full mt-[5px] shrink-0" style="background:#639922;"></span>
        <span class="topic-text">Numeri di ossidazione, ossidi, idruri, idracidi, idrossidi, ossiacidi, sali — IUPAC e tradizionale</span>
      </div>
      <p class="section-head mb-2">// POMERIGGIO</p>
      <div class="flex gap-2 items-start mb-2">
        <span class="w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full mt-[5px] shrink-0" style="background:#639922;"></span>
        <span class="topic-text">Concentrazioni: molarità, molalità, %m/m, %m/V, ppm</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-2 items-start mb-2">
        <span class="w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full mt-[5px] shrink-0" style="background:#639922;"></span>
        <span class="topic-text">Proprietà colligative (abbassamento crioscopico, innalzamento ebullioscopico, pressione osmotica)</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-2 items-start mb-4">
        <span class="w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full mt-[5px] shrink-0" style="background:#639922;"></span>
        <span class="topic-text">Solubilità e soluzioni elettrolitiche</span>
      </div>
      <div class="tip-box pl-3 py-1">
        Per la nomenclatura: fai 20–30 composti da denominare e poi l'inverso (nome → formula).
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Day 5 — Acidi -->
    <div class="day-card p-5 rounded-none">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-4 flex-wrap">
        <span class="badge" style="color:#d05a30;">MER 25</span>
        <span class="day-title">Acidi, basi e reazioni chimiche</span>
        <span class="text-[10px] text-neutral-800 tracking-widest ml-auto">~4–5h</span>
      </div>
      <p class="section-head mb-2">// MATTINA</p>
      <div class="flex gap-2 items-start mb-2">
        <span class="w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full mt-[5px] shrink-0" style="background:#D85A30;"></span>
        <span class="topic-text">Teorie acido-base: Arrhenius, Brønsted-Lowry, Lewis</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-2 items-start mb-2">
        <span class="w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full mt-[5px] shrink-0" style="background:#D85A30;"></span>
        <span class="topic-text">pH, Kw, acidi/basi forti e deboli, calcolo del pH</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-2 items-start mb-4">
        <span class="w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full mt-[5px] shrink-0" style="background:#D85A30;"></span>
        <span class="topic-text">Idrolisi, soluzioni tampone</span>
      </div>
      <p class="section-head mb-2">// POMERIGGIO</p>
      <div class="flex gap-2 items-start mb-2">
        <span class="w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full mt-[5px] shrink-0" style="background:#D85A30;"></span>
        <span class="topic-text">Tipi di reazione: sintesi, scambio semplice/doppio, decomposizione</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-2 items-start mb-4">
        <span class="w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full mt-[5px] shrink-0" style="background:#D85A30;"></span>
        <span class="topic-text">Bilanciamento equazioni, calcolo del pH in esercizi misti</span>
      </div>
      <div class="tip-box pl-3 py-1">
        Concentrati sul calcolo del pH per acidi forti, basi forti, e soluzioni tampone (Henderson-Hasselbalch).
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Day 6 — Termochimica -->
    <div class="day-card p-5 rounded-none">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-4 flex-wrap">
        <span class="badge" style="color:#6d65d4;">GIO 26</span>
        <span class="day-title">Termochimica, teoria cinetica e laboratorio</span>
        <span class="text-[10px] text-neutral-800 tracking-widest ml-auto">~4h</span>
      </div>
      <p class="section-head mb-2">// MATTINA</p>
      <div class="flex gap-2 items-start mb-2">
        <span class="w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full mt-[5px] shrink-0" style="background:#534AB7;"></span>
        <span class="topic-text">Termochimica: entalpia, reazioni eso/endotermiche, legge di Hess</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-2 items-start mb-4">
        <span class="w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full mt-[5px] shrink-0" style="background:#534AB7;"></span>
        <span class="topic-text">Teoria cinetico-molecolare, passaggi di stato, energia cinetica media</span>
      </div>
      <p class="section-head mb-2">// POMERIGGIO</p>
      <div class="flex gap-2 items-start mb-2">
        <span class="w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full mt-[5px] shrink-0" style="background:#534AB7;"></span>
        <span class="topic-text">Laboratorio: DPI, pittogrammi, frasi H e P, schede di sicurezza</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-2 items-start mb-2">
        <span class="w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full mt-[5px] shrink-0" style="background:#534AB7;"></span>
        <span class="topic-text">Tecniche di separazione (filtrazione, distillazione, cromatografia, estrazione)</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-2 items-start mb-4">
        <span class="w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full mt-[5px] shrink-0" style="background:#534AB7;"></span>
        <span class="topic-text">Misure di massa, volume e temperatura; cifre significative</span>
      </div>
      <div class="tip-box pl-3 py-1">
        Il laboratorio è spesso sottovalutato — i pittogrammi GHS e le frasi H escono spesso nelle gare.
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Day 7 — Revisione -->
    <div class="day-card p-5 rounded-none">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-4 flex-wrap">
        <span class="badge" style="color:#555550;">VEN 27</span>
        <span class="day-title">Revisione totale + esercizi da gara</span>
        <span class="text-[10px] text-neutral-800 tracking-widest ml-auto">~5–6h</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-2 items-start mb-2">
        <span class="w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full mt-[5px] shrink-0" style="background:#444440;"></span>
        <span class="topic-text">Ripassi rapidi degli argomenti più deboli</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-2 items-start mb-2">
        <span class="w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full mt-[5px] shrink-0" style="background:#444440;"></span>
        <span class="topic-text">Simula una gara con le prove degli anni precedenti (Giochi della Chimica)</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-2 items-start mb-4">
        <span class="w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full mt-[5px] shrink-0" style="background:#444440;"></span>
        <span class="topic-text">Revisione errori e gap</span>
      </div>
      <div class="tip-box pl-3 py-1">
        SAB 28 = solo ripasso leggero. Non studiare cose nuove il giorno prima.
      </div>
    </div>

  </main>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mt-14 pt-6 border-t border-neutral-900">
    <p class="text-[10px] text-neutral-800 tracking-[0.2em] text-center">[ FINE PIANO · BUONA FORTUNA ]</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
